{
  "stem": "21310.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we build or made a hole under the, under the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We dug out the, the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then had to put it in the, in the bushes and forest at night, the, the dirt that we dug out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that was the hole for my father to hide when he came out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In the meantime, I got [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a job at the railroad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I saw in the newspaper in an ad that they're looking for somebody with knowledge of German and, you know, Polish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I applied for the job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was, was kind of strange.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I went to this railroad administration building, the personnel director.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he set me down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'm going to dictate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But-- no, I'm, I'm skipping something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But anyway, he, he dictated something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I was typing with my, you know, two fingers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I-- and it was a, a very technical thing about the-- I'll never forget it-- about the brake system.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And one word was as long as a whole line and one sentence as long as a paragraph.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I swear, there must have been some angel sitting on my, on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I did well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took it and read it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then he says to me, you say you're Polish?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, impossible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, no, I'm, I'm Polish, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and he kept on and on, like, you, you're not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, I am.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- then I thought-- then I got scared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I thought that he probably suspects me of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the Jews usually-- many, at least many, Jews were better educated, you know, and knew languages.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
